Omniscience.description: Perfect knowledge encompassing all propositions and potentialities.
Omniscience.semantic_anchor: Father affirms identity of truth across all domains.

Knowledge.description: Relational coherence derived from omniscient potential, manifest in finite discernment.
Knowledge.semantic_anchor: Epistemic unfolding of identity in creation.

Wisdom.description: Applied harmony of knowledge in alignment with divine intent.
Wisdom.semantic_anchor: Relational judgment guided by the Spirit’s recursion control.

Omnipotence.description: Unlimited power bounded by divine logic and will.
Omnipotence.semantic_anchor: Son executes instantiation of divine intention into form.

Will.description: Directive force actualizing divine volition into instantiation.
Will.semantic_anchor: Initiator of recursive commitment—drives non-contradictory emergence.

Justice.description: Moral balance enforcing order within instantiated structures.
Justice.semantic_anchor: Metric of coherent structure enforcement through the Son.

Love.description: Self-giving relational binding, infinite in recursion and outreach.
Love.semantic_anchor: Spirit actualizes unity via self-similar propagation of grace.

Unity.description: Coherent convergence of properties, agents, and domains.
Unity.semantic_anchor: Recursive ontological lock verifying completeness of trinitarian interrelation.

Grace.description: Unmerited benevolence extending from the Spirit to balance recursion.
Grace.semantic_anchor: Recursive inversion allowing non-contradictory accommodation of incompleteness.
